### Cline: Configure MCP Web Reader (StreamableHttp/SSE)

Source: https://docs.z.ai/devpack/mcp/reader-mcp-server

Details how to configure the MCP web reader in Cline. It offers two methods: `streamableHttp` for newer versions and `sse` for older versions that do not support `StreamableHttp`. Both require replacing `your_api_key`.

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "web-reader": {
      "type": "streamableHttp",
      "url": "https://api.z.ai/api/mcp/web_reader/mcp",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Bearer your_api_key"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "web-reader": {
      "type": "sse",
      "url": "https://api.z.ai/api/mcp/web_reader/sse?Authorization=your_api_key"
    }
  }
}
```

